text: Gathera is a settlement in Kenya's Central Province about 87 kilometers from the Kenyan capital of Nairobi.http://www.worldplaces.net/ken/01/gathera/ ==Statistics== There is an infant mortality of 44 per 1000 births. Malnutrition is apparent as 1.54% of children below 5 years old are underweight. Most of the land coverage is open broadleaved deciduous forest. The Cultivation Intensity is about 20% cultivated, and 80% natural vegetation.http://www.chinci.com/travel/pax/q/197651/Gathera/KE/Kenya/0/# ==Schools== Gathera Secondary School is located at 2- 10205 Chinga-Kairu Road.http://softkenya.com/directory/gathera-secondary-school/ ==References== Category:Populated places in Central Province (Kenya)
title: Gathera
